  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Anidulafungin may be effective for the treatment of invasive Candida infections. The purpose
      of the study is to find the balance between dose tolerance and effectiveness of several doses
      for the treatment of United States patients with invasive candidiasis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
